hut~
   
{bold}{GREEN}  This bamboo hut is large enough to sleep two or three natives. An{bold}
{bold}{GREEN}  animal skin hangs as a door, which is currently pulled aside allowing{bold}
{bold}{GREEN}  you to see the inside. {BOLD}{BLACK}Nothing of value seems to be located inside,{bold}
{BOLD}{BLACK}  just a few sleeping mats and tools. An unfriendly looking clay mask{bold}
{BOLD}{BLACK}  hangs on the outside wall, next to the door.{bold}

