{bold}{RED}  small pit dug in the sand. Fish have been placed on rocks located{bold}
{bold}{RED}  inside the pit. You can feel t{BOLD}{BLACK}he{bold}{RED} {BOLD}{BLACK}heat radiating from the embers and{bold}
